<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/weibo/user/2831150640" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>深圳卫健委的微博 - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>i@diygod.me (DIYgod)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/crop.14.15.448.448.180/a8bfee30ly8h8w71x1lgbj20d50d5mxt.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1712646987&amp;ssig=2%2BS%2F1%2BvzlH</url><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 04:16:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>1</ttl><item><title>一到春天就鼻痒、爱打喷嚏，容易感冒🤧，小卫提醒大家，这有可能是过敏性鼻炎而非感冒哦[doge]！#过敏性鼻炎和感冒有何区别#？和卫一起看看👇🏻🔹持续时...</title><description>一到春天就鼻痒、爱打喷嚏，容易感冒🤧，小卫提醒大家，这有可能是过敏性鼻炎而非感冒哦&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[doge]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;！&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E9%BC%BB%E7%82%8E%E5%92%8C%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E9%BC%BB%E7%82%8E%E5%92%8C%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#过敏性鼻炎和感冒有何区别#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;？和卫一起看看👇🏻&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔹持续时间&lt;br&gt;①感冒：持续时间一般为7-10天，最长不超过两周；&lt;br&gt;②过敏性鼻炎种类不同，病程会有所区别，一般会大于两周。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔹鼻眼症状&lt;br&gt;①感冒：轻度或中度打喷嚏，流黄鼻涕，无眼睛或皮肤不适；&lt;br&gt;②过敏性鼻炎：打喷嚏较为明显，流清水样鼻涕，眼痒，皮肤瘙痒。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🔹全身症状：&lt;br&gt;①感冒：一般有发烧、食欲减退、肌肉酸痛等症状；&lt;br&gt;②过敏性鼻炎：无发热等全身症状。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（广东疾控）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hokf47n05oj20n20sg761.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O8TLH8vHH</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O8TLH8vHH</guid><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 03:26:59 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>【别再把胃折腾坏了！ #气到胃疼是怎么回事# [抓狂]】饮食重油重盐、情绪焦虑烦躁、长期暴饮暴食……小心你的胃罢工[单身狗]！哪些行为很伤胃？又该如何护胃养胃...</title><description>【别再把胃折腾坏了！ &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B0%94%E5%88%B0%E8%83%83%E7%96%BC%E6%98%AF%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%9B%9E%E4%BA%8B%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E6%B0%94%E5%88%B0%E8%83%83%E7%96%BC%E6%98%AF%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%9B%9E%E4%BA%8B%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#气到胃疼是怎么回事#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[抓狂]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;】饮食重油重盐、情绪焦虑烦躁、长期暴饮暴食……小心你的胃罢工&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[单身狗]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/co_niuec-7d05bc992a.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;！哪些行为很伤胃？又该如何护胃养胃？今天，&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E6%8A%A4%E8%83%83%E6%97%A5%23&amp;amp;isnewpage=1&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#国际护胃日#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;，快转给胃不好的TA👇🏻&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?contai